{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"186549-the-three-little-kittens","title":"Cei trei pi-soi","description":"Celor trei pisoiasi le este frica de câinele din vecini.El vrea să se joace cu ei, dar de câte ori il văd, ei o iau la fugă.De ce credeti că le este atat de frică de el?","language":"Romanian","langCode":"ro","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Marilena Andreescu"],"illustrators":["Youm Kosal"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/186549-the-three-little-kittens"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101318/size3/a997546bf81a177c22005e6474cb2c66.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101318/size6/a997546bf81a177c22005e6474cb2c66.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69716/size6/67fc4ae820996a81ed297a035756af36.jpg","text":"Într-o  bună zi,\ntrei pi-soi \nvăd \nun du-lău.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69717/size6/8b76b882c071045c557571ec4661c990.jpg","text":"Pi-so-i-lor \nle es-te fri-că \nde du-lău.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69718/size6/1f9debea76b9c71f6f98e574a7d6966b.jpg","text":"Pi-so-ii \nfug...","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69719/size6/08185ceaf85ab4ae2a515524f7b83037.jpg","text":"... şi du-lă-ul\n du-pă ei.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69720/size6/9afb6ff01db277c4ff0ca799f6bbfa93.jpg","text":"Pi-so-ii\nfug \nmai re-pe-de, \nsi mai re-pe-de!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69721/size6/72337d3319276e8615f826dfbad328e9.jpg","text":"Pi-so-ii\ndau \npes-te\n o pă-să-ri-că.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69722/size6/4847c79f8fd46dcde685f13b2d1bf527.jpg","text":"Dar pi-so-ii \ntot fug...","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69723/size6/b7a5dbc157065c40a613043be4dd4081.jpg","text":"Pi-so-ii \ndau \npes-te \nun bă-ie-ţel.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69724/size6/122f56cc15ad47248fb9bf6718cc4c99.jpg","text":"Dar pi-so-ii\n tot fug...","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69725/size6/036478a7dd42ba9550718030742176e5.jpg","text":"Fug că-tre \no bu-ca-tă \nlun-gă de lemn.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69726/size6/829bb3114fe17d27d2e5915cbdefc0e9.jpg","text":"- Vai! \nAm în-cur-cat-o!\n-A-ju-tor! \n- A-ju-tor!, stri-gă ei.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69727/size6/191e7331c64d8786bbd54d8545424d10.jpg","text":"Du-lă-ul\na-lear-gă \nzâm-bi-tor \nspre ei.\n- Sunt \na-tât de fe-ri-cit  să a-lerg cu voi!, \nspu-ne el.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69728/size6/64704e0b1d4bb556e21262c5ca42eca4.jpg","text":"Ce sur-pri-ză!\nAcum, \npi-so--ii\nau \nun nou \npri-e-ten.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":13,"words":86}}